{"tid":2159012,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工組開名插 膳心小館 剝削員工","createTime":"2020-08-16T05:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T19:11:11.000Z","uid":32051,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9711d639b7b376510e00c66d38d1006397f62b70","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"【無良 Agape Garden 膳心小館  - 好大嘅官威呀！】<br />\n<br />\n面對揭露黑心黃店，勞工組都掙扎左一段時間，希望盡最後努力溝通，希望拖欠手足代通知金嘅黃店膳心小館可以亡羊補牢，點知膳心小館負責人張小姐唔單止拒絕溝通，仲恐嚇要法律追究打去查詢嘅勞工組成員。<br />\n<br />\n既然溝通不果，勞工組亦唔會對無良老闆客氣，決定揭露黑心僱主膳心小館惡行!<br />\n<br />\n第一罪:明明主動炒人又扮事主自己辭職，借此拒俾七日代通知金<br />\n<br />\n今次被剝削嘅事主五月嘅時候見到膳心小館招募手足，就應徵成為全職樓面員工，一直響膳心工作。直至七月二十八號，總店經理突然告知事主上頭下令要事主即日離職，並且要即時清走locker個人物品。<br />\n<br />\n點知，事主響八月八號到九龍灣膳心總店領取最後一期工資時，卻見到薪金計算表上面白紙黑字寫住事主係&quot;辭職&quot;。薪金計算亦冇包括店方炒人應付嘅七日代通知金。<br />\n<br />\n事主當時同總經理澄清自己唔係主動辭職，而係被炒，所以店方應該要支付代通知金，總理卻話自己話唔到事，叫事主自己同膳心老闆張小姐傾，反覆來回幾個電話中，張小姐一直堅持係事主主動以Whatsapp向經理辭職，但又無法俾出證據。<br />\n<br />\n最後，膳心小館管理層張小姐堅持事主係辭職，並且拒絕再同事主溝通，話有咩就同佢嘅法律顧問講。<br />\n<br />\n#勞法小知識 <br />\n#僱傭條例第49A #須備存工資及僱傭紀錄的規定<br />\n#包括終止合約所需通知期 #無得屈<br />\n#張小姐不如拎封辭職信出嚟睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n第二罪: 薪金組成黑箱作業，離職時被追扣上個月工資<br />\n<br />\n膳心店主張小姐當時俾出嘅七月薪金計算表上，除左冇炒人要俾嘅代通知金，亦離奇地出現左追扣上個月(六月)嘅獎金$500同逐分鐘計嘅遲到罰款119.96。<br />\n<br />\n點解當時六月份唔扣嘅？一炒人就扣，話六月無獎金又遲到又盛？早到有冇計埋先？<br />\n<br />\n#勞法小知識 <br />\n#僱傭條例第32 #扣除工資的限制<br />\n#係無遲到嘅 #案例麥永富訴滙進髮舍 #HCLA422000<br />\n#月薪係包月 #無得扣人遲到<br />\n<br />\n第三罪: 拖欠工資<br />\n<br />\n無論點都好，都需要離職後七日內付清最後一個月人工。但係事主由七月尾離職，到今日八月中仲未收到店方工資，已經違反左法例。<br />\n<br />\n#勞法小知識 <br />\n#僱傭條例第25 #僱傭合約終止時的工資支付<br />\n#任何情況下不得遲於僱傭合約終止後7天支付<br />\n#僱傭條例第26 #支付工資的方式及地點<br />\n#在僱員同意下 #存入該僱員名下的銀行戶口 #或郵政匯票付給<br />\n#無法例規定員工突登搵日上去你到簽收<br />\n#咁鐘意簽收上員工屋企簽囉<br />\n<br />\n顧念膳心小館係知名黃店，響事主向勞工組求助，勞工組出第一個Post之前嘅八月十四日，其實我地都親身打過俾膳心嘅營運總監張小姐了解情況，睇下會唔會有誤會。<br />\n<br />\n點知張小姐態度十分惡劣，又話唔會再回應事件，又話事主係自己辭職，有CCTV為證（但之前張小姐響電話中又同事主堅稱，係事主Whatspp向經理辭職，Whatsapp又點會有CCTV呢？），並且話自己唔會去調解，有咩上勞審庭見。之後仲話會法律追究我地打去嘅勞工組朋友，話有咩就同膳心法律顧問講，真係好大嘅官威。<br />\n<br />\n豈料峰迴路轉，八月十五日勞工組出Post之後，膳心又透過幾位中間人接觸勞工組唔同成員，表示店方會等星期一人事部返工之後聯絡事主作調解，又問事主係咪掌握店方炒人嘅實質證據。<br />\n<br />\n勞工組雖然感謝幾位中間人願意做和事佬，但我地唔明點解膳心小館兩日之間前倨後恭，前一日先話唔會調解、大家庭上見，後一日見到勞工組出左Post就約調解。<br />\n<br />\n我地更加唔明白，點解膳心要透過中間人chok事主係咪掌握證據證明自己係被炒。其實事主係被炒定辭職，膳心心知肚明。之前又話有Whatsapp記錄又話有CCTV證明，前言不對後語，宜家見件事鬧大，又想試探事主有幾多證據響手。對此，勞工組真係非常失望，只見到欺詐同計算，睇唔到店方有真誠地反省自己非法剝削員工嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n我地再重申，黃色經濟圈內唔止有黃店，亦係要撐起響黃店工作嘅手足。<br />\n揭露黃店剝削員工，勞工組都有好多掙扎，但正正係愛之深，責之切，對於黃圈唔好嘅風氣，更唔可以視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n事主的話：<br />\n<br />\n我一直認為返工只求工資，無任何情感。<br />\n<br />\n但自從「黃店」嘅出現，<br />\n我發覺工作以外，更重要嘅係可以選擇為同路人服務，出多一分力<br />\n原來番工都可以講良知，職業都可以講人性<br />\n<br />\n禁堂食令飲食業大受打擊<br />\n無薪假、 cut更、甚至裁員都無可厚非<br />\n因為無一份工包唔炒人，唔係單方面忠誠就得，都受外圍經濟因素影響<br />\n同道理，做生意都無話實包賺<br />\n<br />\n通知期或通知金係保障勞資雙方<br />\n不論咩原因炒人，都要跟足法例<br />\n不論勞資邊一方，該有嘅通知金，該有就要有<br />\n<br />\n聽落都好公平，好實在嘅野<br />\n估唔到會有一個大話冚一個大話，就係為左慳返七日代通知金<br />\n屈人自己辭職，而唔俾代通知金，可以嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家睇到呢到<br />\n<br />\n希望大家放下「黃店永遠是對的」嘅心態<br />\n記得最早期我哋講「黑白是良知、黃藍是政見」<br />\n目的係公平啲咁睇一件事，唔洗以德報怨；以直報怨；以德報德就夠<br />\n面對黑白，真係唔好盲撐！<br />\n<br />\n我認為黃色經濟圈並唔應該剝削自己人 <br />\n而係圈內人互惠互利<br />\n<br />\n「良知」 並唔係口號，更要對自己內部員工都應該有<br />\n係一種實踐！<br />\n<br />\n敢表態做黃店難！做一個有良知、敢於承認錯誤嘅黃店更難！"},{"pid":"37ff070539861096705d32df2e5febcc60a33dd9","tid":2159012,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b02b41342c6e6d81162885ebe307945447a470c0","tid":2159012,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1410d9e274292959cadf7f5ee002562ad230ed48","tid":2159012,"uid":63557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"source？"},{"pid":"2f42e28ae17beffc96b776874ea8612d06aa1732","tid":2159012,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a2df6080dd318a2a27b9a75e9b757b9c2d156de","tid":2159012,"uid":127708,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1410d9e274292959cadf7f5ee002562ad230ed48","tid":2159012,"uid":63557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"source？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1580870672072628/?extid=uh02aG4dcmFVntDE&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1580870672072628%2F%3Fextid%3Duh02aG4dcmFVntDE%26d%3Dn&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=bac1ada3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1580870672072628/?extid=uh02aG4dcmFVntDE&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"beec946166b859211e168b62a9f722dfc9a40598","tid":2159012,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60bfa09c80b6cfce1e4fbdd7ba5b9a0feeebc64","tid":2159012,"uid":98425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"呢間野又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85845fac195784420c5b1a68f416d73c11eed1a6","tid":2159012,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"去勞工處搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21645c72a7d1a8d836aa617fdaa23b6e70dce0f1","tid":2159012,"uid":239561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f8f6582fbecbbee276dfc716eafab11d240d192","tid":2159012,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c29d8c9dfee34b8d0fdaa47ce903bc1c0f1334","tid":2159012,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac342f077f933d82fef2460553c4df4a5e20dff","tid":2159012,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"佢啲連豬蛋卷其實有無授權？"},{"pid":"049d3111a50d8c7de682f76858fdfb2a047e6c65","tid":2159012,"uid":98425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac342f077f933d82fef2460553c4df4a5e20dff","tid":2159012,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"佢啲連豬蛋卷其實有無授權？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"真係唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea48e231a6634257ddf8190138b3284c60c2c677","tid":2159012,"uid":58570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"一日未搞清楚，都係幫襯左其他黃店先"},{"pid":"28a564737d03b9cb873b051fd6701aeb288d39b5","tid":2159012,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢又學渣哥刪留言喎<br />\n見到有苦主喺fb申訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ae91a8e278a93b41589762d0ddab969adc8941","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1581703828655979%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=e5810b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞成咁，唔知到時爆埋真號碼video。<br />\n係咪到時割個店長？"},{"pid":"bbf9fd80e578a7eda82eaa318c71a8a06cbf87b1","tid":2159012,"uid":5994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ae91a8e278a93b41589762d0ddab969adc8941","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1581703828655979%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=e5810b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞成咁，唔知到時爆埋真號碼video。<br />\n係咪到時割個店長？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"又大話冚大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收得皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b66438b6354fc0f07270c710fddf335bab13161","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bbf9fd80e578a7eda82eaa318c71a8a06cbf87b1","tid":2159012,"uid":5994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ae91a8e278a93b41589762d0ddab969adc8941","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1581703828655979%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=e5810b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1581703828655979/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞成咁，唔知到時爆埋真號碼video。<br />\n係咪到時割個店長？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"又大話冚大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收得皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T18:43:22.000Z","msg":"對於勞工組上載聲帶後，我們確認是楊經理的聲音。已即時和楊經理聯絡，再三確認是否有該段對話。很不幸，楊經理確認有此對話。<br />\n<br />\n我們會於8月17日辦公時間內，補發出代通知金。同時，就此向事主及各位朋友道歉，令支持者失望了！對不起！<br />\n<br />\n如前貼文所說，管理層一直所知是前僱員請辭。在8月8日的事件，及14日勞工組聯絡我們後，我們再三向楊經理確認是都同事辭職，甚至，楊經理亦在昨天勞工組facebook留言(見圖)，仍表示是前僱員提出請辭。<br />\n<br />\n一直我們也深怕自己掌握的資訊並不全面，所以在事件曝光前，過五十多小時，嘗試不同渠道向勞工組索取解僱資料、提出進行由第三方主持調解會議;及找前僱員了解，希望有機會得到更多資訊，但一直未如人願，不得要領。而我們最擔心的情況出現了，當聽到聲帶。因為我們知道判斷真的錯了。<br />\n<br />\n這是我們小店管理不善，未能妥善處理此次事件，令很多朋友失望了，除了說對不起，再多也是砌詞狡辯。<br />\n在此，我們向前僱員致歉！<br />\n亦感謝勞工組眾人，鍥而不捨，終於讓我們知道真相！感激！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n割左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3fba276da97b663f6537d834ca21eb2672dd06","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:16:49.000Z","msg":"善心提供參考答案俾膳心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊經理因為想媾女，媾唔到，因愛成恨，欺上瞞下私炒女手足。<br />\n同上邊講條女自己走人，咁膳心當然唔會補水啦。<br />\n膳心乃念楊經理返我地份工搞到媾唔到女，我地決定俾楊經理留任<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f1f6755c540280588ad7fab516dda49ad51a4f","tid":2159012,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"疊埋心水做藍店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bddbed7887118dfa0d36386c2d7801e021578c8","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f1f6755c540280588ad7fab516dda49ad51a4f","tid":2159012,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"疊埋心水做藍店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:24:02.000Z","msg":"不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完當無事發生，好唔好？"},{"pid":"7d5a091b7b08f25f1c5d67b360175271a424b0db","tid":2159012,"uid":92814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:48:43.000Z","msg":"呢排搞乜野呀堆&rdquo;黃店&rdquo;<br />\n真心對膳心好失望，好彩未買月餅，淨係之前買蛋捲"},{"pid":"0d8843a7ca4f04b86bcc6703e45031f89594d189","tid":2159012,"uid":32051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7d5a091b7b08f25f1c5d67b360175271a424b0db","tid":2159012,"uid":92814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:48:43.000Z","msg":"呢排搞乜野呀堆&rdquo;黃店&rdquo;<br />\n真心對膳心好失望，好彩未買月餅，淨係之前買蛋捲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"政治投機<br />\n可惜本質係低賤，都會露底"},{"pid":"f81cf09ece58498b688070b9a9411ab9e6886b99","tid":2159012,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"聽聞啲嘢唔買俾無良嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}